# DirectHandlerTask in rdawn

This guide explains how to use DirectHandlerTask, the most flexible and powerful task type in rdawn.

## Table of Contents

- [Overview](#overview)
- [Basic Usage](#basic-usage)
- [Handler Types](#handler-types)
