### Conditional Logic

```ruby
# Handler with conditional processing
conditional_handler = proc do |input_data, workflow_vars|
  user_type = workflow_vars[:user_type]
  
  case user_type
  when 'premium'
    process_premium_user(input_data)
  when 'standard'
    process_standard_user(input_data)
  when 'trial'
