### Data Transformation

```ruby
# Handler that transforms data structures
transformer_handler = proc do |input_data|
  raw_data = input_data[:raw_data]
  
  # Transform array of hashes
  transformed = raw_data.map do |item|
    {
      id: item['id'],
      name: item['name']&.titleize,
